You can register here. The subject of technical analysis is broad. In this webinar IG’s senior market analyst will narrow things down to what he believes are the most valuable technical analysis indicators for short-term traders to consider. To discuss this and more, join Moneyweb’s Ciaran Ryan and Shaun Murison, senior market analyst for IG Markets SA, in this webinar taking place on Wednesday, February 8 at 11:00. Register for this webinar here. Discussion points: More on the guest: Shaun Murison
Senior market analyst for IG  Murison has worked in financial markets for 15 years, previously running IG’s Durban branch in South Africa, before moving to Johannesburg. Murison now works as a senior market analyst for IG, providing research and regular market commentary across all forms of media. He is a registered person on the Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE) and a certified financial technician (CFTe).